dataRoles.name: values
dataRoles.description: Databind a list of values that appear in the slider. Values must be numeric and will be automatically sorted in ascending order.

defaultSelectedValue.description: The default selected value when the report is first loaded. Set to -12000 to default to no filter.

barWidth.description: Change the whidth of the bar

handlerFontSize.description: Change the font size of the handler
